slindak (0.1.6) unstable; urgency=low

  * New version.

  [ Alexander Shishkin ]
  * version bump
  * add rm_rf() implementation from grasp
  * move common things to library constructor
  * added stubs for testing framework
  * slindak: do not bail on unspecified query format
  * slindweb: don't reinitialize output
  * testsuite: use /dev/null as commands' stderr/stdout
  * add dpkg_source() and dpkg_deb() implementations
  * simple yet functional framework for regression testing
  * slindak: add list query functionality

 -- Alexander Shishkin <virtuoso@slind.org>  Tue, 19 Feb 2008 13:40:47 +0300

